  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JUST A GAME</h2>Try to beat as many waves as possible. You can't regen your health. earn money by killing balls and buy turrets and bombs<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upcoming Content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>-More weapons;<br></li><li>-More game modes;<br></li><li>-More items and various other content that will bring more fun into the game.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>During a secret experiment, a big mistake was made and deadly balls spread across the world, you are the only one who can stop it.(or you are not, we don't actually know that)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Balls</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Normal Ball</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/891090/extras/b19717799a1ecb0baa87c759ba8fbcd1.poster.avif?t=1713047692\" width=50 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/891090/extras/b19717799a1ecb0baa87c759ba8fbcd1.webm?t=1713047692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/891090/extras/b19717799a1ecb0baa87c759ba8fbcd1.mp4?t=1713047692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It'll kill you by taking you in its body. <br>Its weakest point is its eyes.<br>Speed 10<br>Health 100<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast Ball</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/891090/extras/000d8aa4d28c1a7e8df7ef694cafe0ee.poster.avif?t=1713047692\" width=54 height=48 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/891090/extras/000d8aa4d28c1a7e8df7ef694cafe0ee.webm?t=1713047692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/891090/extras/000d8aa4d28c1a7e8df7ef694cafe0ee.mp4?t=1713047692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It'll kill you by taking you in its body. <br>Its weakest point is its eyes(and this ball is a little stupid).<br>Speed 20<br>Health 100<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shop</h2>You can buy Turret,Bomb,Medkit and Speed syringe.",
